                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "Wing %@ links %lld to %lld, and wing %@ links %lld to %lld." : {
            "comment" : "A list of 4 items. The first item is a description of the pivot. The second item is a description of the first wing. The third item is a description of the second wing. The fourth item is a description of the secondary condition. The first argument is the string “R%1$argC%2$arg”. The fourth argument is the string “R%1$argC%2$arg”.",
